  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK463">
<l>ākkaṅ karuti mutaliḻakkuñ ceyviṉai</l>
<l>yūkkā raṟivuṭai yār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wise men will not, in the hopes of profit, undertake works that will consume their principal.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
